This color theme for iTerm2 is made to match the theme with similar name in TextMate.
To use it, simply clone into the repo, or download the file under "Download". When you have the `Espresso Libre.itermcolors` file on your hard drive, double click to install in iTerm.

This code is offered under public domain. Use it, modify it, redistribute it or do what ever you feel like doing with XML.

It looks like this:
![colours](https://github.com/mbadolato/iTerm2-Color-Schemes/raw/master/screenshots/espresso_libre.png)

